Company Description: Founded IN 1948, Mcdonald's Is One Of The Leading Food Service Retailers IN The World. With One Of Its Outlets Based IN Brooklyn, N.Y., It Operates Through More Than 32,000 Eateries IN 117 Countries. The Restaurant Chain Serves Various Food Products, Including Fries, Burgers, Chicken Nuggets, Salads, Wraps And Sandwiches. Additionally, Mcdonald's Offers Beverages, Such As Milk Jug, Iced Tea, Roast Coffee, Shakes And Smoothies. The Chain Also Provides Meal Bundles, Including The Dollar Menu, Extra Value Meals, Happy Meals And Mighty Kids Meals For Families And Children.
